{"tid":996683,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"你哋會點樣追好耐冇見同聯絡嘅中學同學？","createTime":"2019-01-26T13:20:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-26T14:19:34.000Z","uid":4379,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"159863bdec7e512d11bf89e2818022f34f68de2d","tid":996683,"uid":4379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T13:20:51.000Z","msg":"最近想追返一個坐咗喺佢後面三年但係對話唔多過十句嘅同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇巴打絲打有好方法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本身同佢唔係太熟，係小學同校中學同班所以先叫做知有依個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 近排趁佢po snapchat嘅時候覆咗佢，叫做開咗個頭咁，不過我同佢嘅話題都離唔開讀書同佢養嘅嗰隻貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n暫時問過佢啲frd話佢鐘意睇下小説、打羽毛球壁球、撚下小動物、扮下靚咁，有冇巴打絲打可以分享/教下我點樣可以易啲再進一步？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e06101b76aa31c86cfee936aaee3d4d87252cf3b","tid":996683,"uid":88167,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T13:22:24.000Z","msg":"你個名都答左你啦，收手啦"},{"pid":"ea4af34986d514cbb11e898a2cb6263cf4325861","tid":996683,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T13:23:21.000Z","msg":"Hi<br />\nGo tea?<br />\nOk"},{"pid":"6c03547a5b6ce77e2b8b83ae6946d4581157582a","tid":996683,"uid":4379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e06101b76aa31c86cfee936aaee3d4d87252cf3b","tid":996683,"uid":88167,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T13:22:24.000Z","msg":"你個名都答左你啦，收手啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T13:23:55.000Z","msg":"名嚟姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你俾我再掙扎多一次"},{"pid":"c4bdb872865304062241ed86207ae77178c7d5e8","tid":996683,"uid":93136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea4af34986d514cbb11e898a2cb6263cf4325861","tid":996683,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T13:23:21.000Z","msg":"Hi<br />\nGo tea?